  "rationale": "CPacket is a plain aggregate of dst/src endpoints and the message payload \u2014 all three are spec-meaningful (network specs routinely inspect sender, receiver, and message). Each field is projected through its own View impl so semantic equality (e.g., endpoint wire identity, message content modulo representation) is honoured rather than relying on structural `==`.",
